{"tid":458813,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都鍾意儲股收息？","createTime":"2017-11-05T08:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T04:16:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"250195db671778eaf04d07ad171b8ed1818aad97","tid":458813,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"其實上一代經濟起飛, 要致富, 買樓收租, 買鋪收租<br />\n我識一個阿叔, 他都是基層出身, 和親戚在九十年代在銅鑼灣夾份買鋪收租, 1x年賣了鋪位, 現在幾千家身家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又或者買穩定有增長的實業的股份, 如長實, 匯豐, 新鴻基, 中電等<br />\n80年代起, 每個月有錢便買, 每年股價升和有股息收<br />\n真人真事, 有些上左年紀的人便是這樣每個月做這個簡單的動作便發達了</span><br />\n<br />\n簡單總結<br />\n上一代(50, 60後), 往往因為賭, 黃, 大洗, 毒(排名有先後), 把錢用晒<br />\n好多時窮人都不是大洗, 但往往把錢用晒<br />\n而稍有學識/眼光/常識的人, 就把錢用來買可以錢變錢的東西. 時間日子一久, 距離便愈來愈大<br />\n其實上一代經濟起飛, 買一些正路和正常的東西, 都已經年年錢搵錢. 現在這個年代則周圍都是騙局, 和上一代很不同<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;<br />\n樂觀sir都推介咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4368f3e079755616fbe906c0b66904040979b5a","tid":458813,"uid":155949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實上一代經濟起飛, 要致富, 買樓收租, 買鋪收租<br />\n我識一個阿叔, 他都是基層出身, 和親戚在九十年代在銅鑼灣夾份買鋪收租, 1x年賣了鋪位, 現在幾千家身家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又或者買穩定有增長的實業的股份, 如長實, 匯豐, 新鴻基, 中電等<br />\n80年代起, 每個月有錢便買, 每年股價升和有股息收<br />\n真人真事, 有些上左年紀的人便是這樣每個月做這個簡單的動作便發達了</span><br />\n<br />\n簡單總結<br />\n上一代(50, 60後), 往往因為賭, 黃, 大洗, 毒(排名有先後), 把錢用晒<br />\n好多時窮人都不是大洗, 但往往把錢用晒<br />\n而稍有學識/眼光/常識的人, 就把錢用來買可以錢變錢的東西. 時間日子一久, 距離便愈來愈大<br />\n其實上一代經濟起飛, 買一些正路和正常的東西, 都已經年年錢搵錢. 現在這個年代則周圍都是騙局, 和上一代很不同<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n樂觀sir都推介咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得岩<br />\n每個月都儲股 收息<br />\n可惜股息被要求拎去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e211187a468668389349a97baa3b088722edba07","tid":458813,"uid":93900,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"上一代(50, 60後), 往往因為賭, 黃, 大洗, 毒(排名有先後), 把錢用晒<br />\n好多時窮人都不是大洗, 但往往把錢用晒<br />\n而稍有學識/眼光/常識的人, 就把錢用來買可以錢變錢的東西. 時間日子一久, 距離便愈來愈大<br />\ncannot agree more<br />\n屋企人成日賭錢 結果就退休都仙都唔仙下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3fdd45ffd9a44f81749b5207a0b536dfd4edb9","tid":458813,"uid":22422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:03:31.000Z","msg":"最撚好笑係<br />\n啲死老嘢調番轉話後生玩股票係賭錢<br />\n咁過大海 游乾水 進貢馬會呢啲又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f4a4f508062c28aea9abb2f750382d3a73dc91","tid":458813,"uid":90863,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服"},{"pid":"7448099ca5bbfc81d5543b77bbf4201781a3540a","tid":458813,"uid":93900,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n之前d樓咁平 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9f85845a33706ba2001dd7f73d31fb9eaf161b","tid":458813,"uid":90863,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n之前d樓咁平 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講係咁講<br />\n但同時好多其他草根淨係識亂咁fing錢又攞去賭"},{"pid":"2cc7c73cad9e09ae4504a26f49b324ecfb5ca2d9","tid":458813,"uid":41923,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n之前d樓咁平 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講係咁講<br />\n但同時好多其他草根淨係識亂咁fing錢又攞去賭</blockquote><br />\n窮人特質<br />\n<br />\n1. 對至親仔女刻薄至極 用/食好少少就要日屌夜屌 平時成日計埋d縮數虐待自己仔女<br />\n但對支那蝗親戚就死要面扮大方 自己窮到無飯開貼錢比蝗親戚<br />\n<br />\n2. 極怕負債 叫佢地做按揭買樓就話唔敢揹條債上身 計完數又話個個月比幾千蚊利息銀行賺好on居<br />\n但賭錢賭輸左借貴利財仔時又變左唔識計數<br />\n<br />\n3. 極怕持有現以外任何資產 叫佢買股票 跌左零點幾%就好似你殺佢全家咁 更莫講話買樓 淨係識迴避風險<br />\n但過大海賭錢/打麻雀/馬會時絕不手軟長輸長買"},{"pid":"2af7d3cbe1bbd3956fc0bcb7fad3dd8859175e11","tid":458813,"uid":41923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n之前d樓咁平 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講係咁講<br />\n但同時好多其他草根淨係識亂咁fing錢又攞去賭</blockquote><br />\n窮人特質<br />\n<br />\n1. 對至親仔女刻薄至極 用/食好少少就要日屌夜屌 平時成日計埋d縮數虐待自己仔女<br />\n但對支那蝗親戚就死要面扮大方 自己窮到無飯開貼錢比蝗親戚<br />\n<br />\n2. 極怕負債 叫佢地做按揭買樓就話唔敢揹條債上身 計完數又話個個月比幾千蚊利息銀行賺好on居<br />\n但賭錢賭輸左借貴利財仔時又變左唔識計數<br />\n<br />\n3. 極怕持有現<span style=\"color: red;\">金</span>以外任何資產 叫佢買股票 跌左零點幾%就好似你殺佢全家咁 更莫講話買樓 淨係識迴避風險<br />\n但過大海賭錢/打麻雀/馬會時絕不手軟長輸長買</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6dc525bf27b5251905f8f693b93665c705b4e5c0","tid":458813,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚好笑係<br />\n啲死老嘢調番轉話後生玩股票係賭錢<br />\n咁過大海 游乾水 進貢馬會呢啲又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n股票係長時間眼界考驗<br />\n馬會賭輸就係賭輸<br />\n識玩一定玩 股票"},{"pid":"6a96ffddf6a76bba85f913443c95df2ad5777b95","tid":458813,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"儲緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287c75c7dcf529f060c883bc8df8f7f7b9230f3c","tid":458813,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"以前既話係買樓好過"},{"pid":"86f8597d2772fcf4374164890c8a777f492d47f2","tid":458813,"uid":4285,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"我身邊都好多八十後但好撚老土, 一講股票, <br />\n<br />\n就話你投機乜柒, 又話自己唔會玩&quot;呢D野&quot;<br />\n<br />\n講多都廢事, 由佢地拎住越黎越唔見駛嘅現金啦, 哈"},{"pid":"8747212284a9995a7b6ea97c8c30e0e66e245b1c","tid":458813,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986e8120620f2c2ff50d54513119ccebbe35afc5","tid":458813,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e681383d91bf2cc84c84afe52ad92a1693edf72c","tid":458813,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n之前d樓咁平 點同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講係咁講<br />\n但同時好多其他草根淨係識亂咁fing錢又攞去賭</blockquote><br />\n窮人特質<br />\n<br />\n1. 對至親仔女刻薄至極 用/食好少少就要日屌夜屌 平時成日計埋d縮數虐待自己仔女<br />\n但對支那蝗親戚就死要面扮大方 自己窮到無飯開貼錢比蝗親戚<br />\n<br />\n2. 極怕負債 叫佢地做按揭買樓就話唔敢揹條債上身 計完數又話個個月比幾千蚊利息銀行賺好on居<br />\n但賭錢賭輸左借貴利財仔時又變左唔識計數<br />\n<br />\n3. 極怕持有現以外任何資產 叫佢買股票 跌左零點幾%就好似你殺佢全家咁 更莫講話買樓 淨係識迴避風險<br />\n但過大海賭錢/打麻雀/馬會時絕不手軟長輸長買</blockquote><br />\n個個都咁醒既時候...仲邊有窮人"},{"pid":"67f6b7b4b91ab76f9a9c6e1faeb8620531d12ee8","tid":458813,"uid":89857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f998f5e3ea6cb6e50d0855d4c49be9020e6398","tid":458813,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"345"},{"pid":"d5e148997e897026fdb48c6e2196abe45c475ff6","tid":458813,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:45:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講得岩<br />\n每個月都儲股 收息<br />\n可惜股息被要求拎去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實咁都唔錯，即係每年有人請去旅行<br />\n<br />\n儲還儲又唔好逼得自己太緊咁先可以長久"},{"pid":"485d585a776753ab61db709518637a68e5d49ebb","tid":458813,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我儲美股，好多大公司真係每年加派息<br />\n<br />\n仲多過人工加得個幾%"},{"pid":"ea2cf0a49b672e229fa5d1b213c13dd3dfbefd99","tid":458813,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我儲美股，好多大公司真係每年加派息<br />\n<br />\n仲多過人工加得個幾%</blockquote><br />\n波音 3M <br />\n指數成分股大把好公司<br />\n買佢哋股票又唔使搞到月供咁撚麻煩"},{"pid":"665226723fa070e5b09b0a6ff319c34097c0be88","tid":458813,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母識儲錢<br />\n所以草根階層都捱到兩層樓<br />\n好佩服</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情況類似，當年呀爺個代同幾個兄弟做生意叫購到錢，咁佢將賺既錢投放落票股巿場。到後期己經 Feel 到個行業息微，之後把心一橫賣盤套現投入股票巿場。去到我老豆個代己經睇到分別，佢既叔伯有 D 自己開檔野，當然有成功有失敗。去到我個代雖然唔算大富大貴，但起碼叫做中規中矩。我既堂叔既有部份發大達，住緊獨立屋有司機接送，環境差既要住公屋申請綜緩。"},{"pid":"fc0c236373291f431c62da30bb45fedb21ff3c61","tid":458813,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"高質post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8f2c46c7309253d992960986d61552dc31b8f7","tid":458813,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我儲美股，好多大公司真係每年加派息<br />\n<br />\n仲多過人工加得個幾%</blockquote><br />\n波音 3M <br />\n指數成分股大把好公司<br />\n買佢哋股票又唔使搞到月供咁撚麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩年代啊<br />\n大貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n銀行股買WFC啦"},{"pid":"d7e095b7c277c84ddeb53ac805b6c6b6a6a2c014","tid":458813,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T03:17:59.000Z","msg":"我都想每月有錢剩去買股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家可能要儲一年先有啲餘錢去買一手煤氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n供樓搞到冇乜多餘錢去買股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}